[SN]TITLE[SN]
Simon Johnson death: Man charged with murder

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been charged with murdering a man found at home with fatal stab wounds, police said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Simon Johnson, 41, was attacked at his home in Cradley Road, Netherton, Dudley, in August 2016.
Damilola Johnson, 18,  will appear before Walsall magistrates next month, West Midlands Police said.
A 16-year-old boy has previously been charged with murder and another 16 year old has been charged with burglary.
